      "acceptanceCriteria": "CFD solver must be version-controlled with documented regression tests and a traceable build record.",
      "rationale": "ANSYS Fluent 2022R2 was used under an ISO 9001-certified software quality plan. Version control records and regression test logs confirm compliance with the required level for MRL 2."
