      "acceptanceCriteria": "Grid convergence index (GCI) must be reported for the relative hemolysis index QoI and must not exceed 5%.",
      "rationale": "A three-level mesh refinement study was conducted. GCI for the relative hemolysis index was 2.8% on the medium mesh (12.4 million cells), which was adopted for all production runs."
