      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 2,
      "achievedLevel": 3,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Predicted relative hemolysis index must agree with experimental measurements within ±15% across all operating points.",
      "rationale": "CFD predictions of RH agreed with FDA experimental measurements within ±9% across all 5 operating points. The model consistently identified the same worst-case condition (6 L/min, 3500 RPM) as the experimental data."
    },
    {
