      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "The QoI used in validation (relative hemolysis index) must be the same metric used in the regulatory decision.",
      "rationale": "The relative hemolysis index (RH) is the primary regulatory acceptance criterion (RH < 1 vs. predicate). Validation data and model outputs both report RH directly, ensuring full alignment."
