      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Validation activities must use the same pump geometry family and operating regime as the COU device.",
      "rationale": "Validation was performed on the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump geometry, which is the same device family as the COU. Operating conditions (flow rate, rotational speed, fluid properties) were matched to CPB clinical use."
