    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. The 6 not-assessed factors are appropriately scoped out per ASME V&V 40 MRL 2 requirements. Monte Carlo UQ confirms the 95th-percentile relative hemolysis index (0.87) satisfies the RH < 1 acceptance criterion with margin. The model is judged credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device.",
